description: After having been on the air for almost a year, The folks from the paranormal TV show, Paranormal State. on A&E join Darkness Radio to catch up on where things are now and where the show is headed!  Ryan Buell, Katrina Weidman, Heather Taddy, Sergey Poberezhny, and Eilfie Music all appear in this episode!
